MRP = The Matrix.org Resurrection Project

The project that migrates data from the old Matrix.org forum into MySQL database and builds a Ruby on Rails application to browse and query on them.

Features:
- Browse by categories and forums. [DONE]
- Search by subject, author, forum and creation date. [DONE]
- Search by full-text. [PENDING]
- Some of the markups (e.g. [mop 253]). [PENDING]

All the other requests will NOT be implemented for now.